title: Slingo Quest Hawaii.rar
description: Enjoy Slingo fun in paradise! The classic and addictive combination of Slots and Bingo jets off to the beautiful Hawaiian Islands and takes Slingo to a whole new level! Lie on the beach and order up some Slingo Tricks like Summon Joker and Pattern Match. Dive beneath the waves to a coral reef and discover Platinum Coins and Tiki Jokers. Hike up the secret volcano and take on the Tiki Guy in a game of Volcano Slingo. Take a Slingo vacation today!
